Package com.phunware.mapping

Contains the basic classes and helper classes for MaaS Mapping SDK

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    PwOnBuildingDataListener
    Used as a callback for when map data has been loaded.
    PwOnPOIDataListener
    Callback for getting Points of Interest (POIs) for a building.
    PwOnPOITypesDownloadListener
    Callback for getting Point of Interest(POI) types mapping
    PwOnSegmentDownloadListener
    Callback for getting segments for a building
    PwOnSvgDownloadCallback
    Callback for getting SVG image data.
    PwRouteCallback
    Callback for getting route data.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    PwMappingModule
    Retrieves an instance of the PwMappingModule to install into the MaaS Core session.
    PwMappingUtils
    Convenience methods to help with common operations on building and point data.
